	<h1 class="news">Statewide school closure</h1>
	<div id="divider"></div>
	<div id="newsWrap">
    <div id="newsArticle">
        <p class="date">April 9, 2020</p>
    <p>Staff, parents and families,</p>

<p><br>
Governor Parson &amp; Commissioner Vandeven just made the announcement of schools statewide closing for the remainder of our approved calendar year. LJC6 has received the information at the same moment each of you have during this daily press conference today. My administrative staff will work as quickly as we can to communicate what this means to the district as a whole, each class and each individual student. We know there will be many questions and we will work to get you specific information as soon as we have it for you.<br><br>
Stay safe, stay well, we miss you and we care about you.<br>
Kathy Butler</p>
